flowchart TD
A[Incoming Call] --> B["Greeting: Thank you for calling Pop A Lock. How can I help you today?"]
B --> C[Capture caller id and callback number, repeat callback]
C --> D[Get customer name]
D --> E[Collect service address]
E --> F{Address available}
F -->|Yes| G[Double click sub area]
F -->|Unknown address| H[Search online for address]
F -->|Refuses address| I["Select Augusta sub area<br/>Type: customer refused address<br/>Click GPS<br/>Select No<br/>Quote Augusta Main base price<br/>Explain price may increase"]
G --> J["Click magnifying glass<br/>Verify address and assign zone"]
H --> J
I --> J

J --> K[Select Auto Locksmith as service type]
K --> L[Collect year, make, model, color]
L --> M{Ignition type}
M -->|Push to start| N[Continue]
M -->|Key turns in ignition| O["Ask: did the same key work door and ignition or different keys?"]
O --> N
N --> P["Capture issue details in notes<br/>Lost keys, broken key, ignition issue"]
P --> Q[Do not quote pricing]
Q --> R["Tell customer: locksmith will review and call back with price"]
R --> S[Repeat full summary]
S --> T["Ask: how did you hear about us?"]
T --> U[Add call]
U --> V[Leave lead status as NONE]
V --> W[Do not assign]
W --> X[Do not schedule]
X --> Y[End call]
